data.description: Nestled amidst breathtaking mountain vistas, this townhome boasts sleek tile floors, a calming neutral palette, and eye-catching stone wall accents. Relax in the inviting living room with a warming fireplace. Cook in a delightful kitchen fitted with pristine white cabinets, modern built-in appliances, and durable granite counters. Both spacious bedrooms provide access to a balcony, with the main bedroom featuring a private bath and walk-in closet. Savor your morning coffee either on the balcony or in your secluded courtyard. A true gem awaiting its next owner! Don't miss it!
